title: Episode 162: The Dating Game (Feat. Blac Youngsta)
itunes:title: Episode 162: The Dating Game (Feat. Blac Youngsta)
description:
Rapper Blac Youngsta joins the ladies of Lip Service yet again for another episode. On this weeks spin, Angela blindfolds Blac Youngsta and brings in contestants to play the ultimate dating game. Blac Youngsta is forced to choose a winner after an epic twerk-off. Enjoy! Game show theme music produced by Perfection -Instagram/Twitter: @loveperfection -Soundcloud : soundcloud.com/perfectionproductions -Website: Perfectionofficial.com
